dataset.title: Dactylogyrids (Platyhelminthes: Monogenea) from the gills of the African carp, Labeo coubie Rüppell (Cyprinidae), from Senegal, with descriptions of three new species of Dactylogyrus and the redescription of Dactylogyrus cyclocirrus Paperna, 1973

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Musilová, Na Ď A, Ehulková, Eva Ř, Gelnar, Milan (2009): Dactylogyrids (Platyhelminthes: Monogenea) from the gills of the African carp, Labeo coubie Rüppell (Cyprinidae), from Senegal, with descriptions of three new species of Dactylogyrus and the redescription of Dactylogyrus cyclocirrus Paperna, 1973. Zootaxa 2241: 47-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.190572
